Order of Law
/Ancient-Aetherium/placeholder.png
Any time the law of Prince is specifically broken, the law breaker must be brought down or turned in. Doing so upholds the Order of Law

Order of Obedience
/Ancient-Aetherium/placeholder.png
Those who take the Order of Obedience vow to never break one of Princes Laws or risk becoming a Sinner of Prince.

Order of Destruction
/Ancient-Aetherium/placeholder.png
Any time a member of the Hive is spotted, and can be reasonably engaged in combat, they must be destroyed to maintain the Order of Destruction.